  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_commissioning_data_sets_introduction">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_commissioning_data_sets_introduction">CDS</xref>) are maintained and developed by the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>, in accordance with the needs of the NHS and the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_commissioning_data_sets_introduction">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>
 form the basis of data on 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
 carried out by 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATIONS</xref>
 reported centrally for monitoring and payment purposes. They support the current 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_healthcare_resource_group">Healthcare Resource Group</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_healthcare_resource_group">HRG</xref>) version for calculation of payment to trusts and monitoring of other initiatives.        </p>
      <p>
Requests for changes to the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_commissioning_data_sets_introduction">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>
 should be submitted via email to 
              <xref href="mailto:enquiries@nhsdigital.nhs.uk"
               scope="external"
               format="html">enquiries@nhsdigital.nhs.uk, </xref>
stating "Commissioning Data Sets" in the subject line.        </p>
      <p>
Current versions of the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_commissioning_data_sets_introduction">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>
 can be found at 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_commissioning_data_set_versions">Commissioning Data Set Versions</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_commissioning_data_sets_introduction">Commissioning Data Sets</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_commissioning_data_sets_overview">Commissioning Data Sets Overview</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
